{"word":"ἀστραπή","slug":"ἀστραπή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀστραπή</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀστεροπή, στεροπή</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a flash of lightning, lightning</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>lightnings</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>any bright light</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}